<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Hello Team !&nbsp;</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>{!Bug_Log__c.CreatedBy}&nbsp;</b>says that :&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">"{!Bug_Log__c.Type__c} on&nbsp;<b><font color="#990000">{!Bug_Log__c.App__c}</font>&nbsp;</b>related to the&nbsp;{!Bug_Log__c.Object__c}"</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">To be more precised,&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">"{!Bug_Log__c.Description__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Can you check for me, please ?</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">It is&nbsp;<b>{!Bug_Log__c.PrioritySeverity__c}&nbsp;</b>and according to me it should be resolved on&nbsp;<b>{!Bug_Log__c.Expected_Date__c}</b>."</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Team, please go to Easy Log and check for the&nbsp;<b>{!Bug_Log__c.Name}&nbsp;</b>to resolve&nbsp;<b>{!Bug_Log__c.CreatedBy}</b>&nbsp;'s issue.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">Follow the link :&nbsp;</font></font><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;</font></font><font face="arial" size="2" style="font-family: arial;">https://carmignac-crm.lightning.force.com/</font><font face="arial" size="2" style="font-family: arial;">lightning/r/Bug_Log__c/{!Bug_Log__c.Id}/view</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><font face="arial" size="2" style="font-family: arial;"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">And do not forget to&nbsp;<b>Assigned</b>&nbsp;the request to you, if you decide to resolve it :-)&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="">Good Luck&nbsp;!</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>